The Development Process using Git
1.Fork(own to you)
2.git clone
3.git remote add upstream https://github.com/原作者/项目名.git
4.develop,fix
5.git add .
6.git commit -m "x"
7.git push

to update:
1.git fetch upstream        # 下载更新，不动代码
2.git merge upstream/main   # 合并更新
3.git push origin main      # 同步到Github(fork的项目)

pull requests:
1.git checkout -b dev
2.change
3.git add .
4.git commit -m "x"
5.git push origin dev
